SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY CAST(order_items_status AS STRING),CAST(order_items_created_month AS STRING)) as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY order_items_created_month DESC, z__pivot_col_rank, order_items_status) AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN order_items_shipped_year IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, order_items_shipped_year, CASE WHEN order_items_shipped_week IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, order_items_shipped_week) AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM order_items.shipped_at )) AS order_items_shipped_year,
        (FORMAT_DATE('%F', DATE_TRUNC(order_items.shipped_at , WEEK(MONDAY)))) AS order_items_shipped_week,
    order_items.status  AS order_items_status,
        (FORMAT_TIMESTAMP('%Y-%m', order_items.created_at , 'US/Eastern')) AS order_items_created_month,
    COUNT(*) AS order_items_count
FROM `looker-private-demo.thelook.order_items`  AS order_items
WHERE (( ((( (DATE(order_items.created_at , 'US/Eastern'))  ) >= ((DATE_ADD(CURRENT_DATE('US/Eastern'), INTERVAL -7 DAY))) AND ( (DATE(order_items.created_at , 'US/Eastern'))  ) < ((DATE_ADD(DATE_ADD(CURRENT_DATE('US/Eastern'), INTERVAL -7 DAY), INTERVAL 7 DAY))))) )

  )
GROUP BY
    1,
    2,
    3,
    4) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 500 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank
